```python
def maxSumSubarray(nums):
    n = len(nums)
    dp = [[float('-inf')] * (n + 1) for _ in range(n)]
    dp[0][0] = nums[0]
    for i in range(1, n):
        dp[i][0] = nums[i]
    for i in range(1, n):
        for j in range(i, n):
            dp[i][j] = max(dp[i-1][j], dp[i][j-1]) + nums[i]
    return max(dp[n-1])
```
